quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,184,"Hulee On Tagu…óo on, o tagu adinoongu ngun"
  26,185,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Pellet, an ko a jeyaa…óo mbil…óaa…ďe …ďen"
  26,186,"An a wonaali si wanaa …ďanndunke yeru amen, tawde me…óen jikkumaa ko a jeyaa…óo e fenu…ďe …ďen"
  26,187,"Awa fukku e dow amen kunte kammu ngun, si tawii a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ďe …ďen"
  26,188,"O maaki: \"Ko Joomi am woni Anndu…óo ko golloton kon"
  26,189,"∆Āe fenni mo, nanngi …ďe Lepte √Īalaande …óowdiinde nden. Pellet, …óen laatino Lepte √Īalaande mawnde"
  26,190,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,191,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  26,192,"E pellet, kayre ko nde jippinaande Jooma winndere nden"
  26,193,Jippinii nde Ruuhu hoolaa…óo on
  26,194,Ka …ďernde maa…óa fii yo a laato jeyaa…óo e jertinoo…ďe …ďen
  26,195,E …óemngal Aarabu …ďanngungal
  26,196,"Pellet, kayre hinde ka …óeri aran…ďe …ďen"
  26,197,"Enee, hara laatanaaki …ďe Maande, nde tawata anndiino nde …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila anndu…ďe …ďen"
  26,198,Sinndo Men jippinno nde e dow yoga e ajamiyankoo…ďe …ďen
  26,199,"o janngi nde e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe laatotaako gom…óin…ďe nde"
  26,200,Ko wano nii Men naadiri …óum e …ďer…óe bon…ďe …ďen
  26,201,"∆Āe gom…óintaa nde, haa …ďe yi'a Lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  26,202,"∆äe ara e ma…ď…ďe e juhayee, hara …ďe so'aa"
  26,203,"Sakko …ďe wi'a: \"Taw si ko men nennantee…ďe"
  26,204,"Enee, ko Lepte Amen …óen …ďe he√Īorta"
  26,205,A tinii si Men dakmitii …ďe duu…ďi
  26,206,Refti ari e ma…ď…ďe kon ko …ďe laatinoo hi…ďe fodee
